OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOccasional showers heavy and
OL,6,Fwintry at times. Some bright spells
OL,7,Fand sunny intervals developing between
OL,8,Fshowers at times. A rather cold day,
OL,9,Fwith fresh westerly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA few showers this evening,
OL,12,Fstill wintry on high ground, then
OL,13,Fbecoming dry overnight with clear
OL,14,Fspells. Winds easing and allowing a
OL,15,Ftouch of frost.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FA dry and bright day with some
OL,18,Fhazy sunshine at times, the best in
OL,19,Fthe morning with high cloud thickening
OL,20,Fin the afternoon. Lighter winds, a
OL,21,Fgentle southerly later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
